beer.beer_description:
A single hop Pale Ale made using HBC 586 Cryo Hops to show the power and glory of Cryo!

Bursting with the tropical flavours of lychee, mango, & citrus with slight herbal undertones and a beautiful light back end malt balance.

Cryo Hops are a new hop that have been created and processed in a way that provide the brewer with a concentrated hop pellet loaded with all the good aromas and flavours (oils & lupulin) you want in a beer.

It's a win for the brewer and the drinker!
